nh gi\u1ecfi... gi\u00fap h\u1ecdc sinh thi \u0111\u1ed7 v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 cao<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody class=\"row-striping row-hover\">\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<!-- #tablepress-35 from cache --><\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"1Tai_sao_can_gia_su_lop_la_cho_be\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #ed1c24; font-size: 100%;\"><strong>1.T\u1ea1i sao c\u1ea7n gia s\u01b0 l\u1edbp l\u00e1 cho b\u00e9?<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">\u00a0B\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n con c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch c\u1ea7m vi\u1ebft t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t?<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">\u00a0B\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n con h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng th\u00f3i quen h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp t\u1ed1t?<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1149\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1149\" style=\"width: 600px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-1149 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/loi_khuyen_gia_su_tieu_hoc.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"424\" srcset=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/loi_khuyen_gia_su_tieu_hoc.jpg 600w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/loi_khuyen_gia_su_tieu_hoc-300x212.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1149\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 Gia s\u01b0 cho b\u00e9 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb v\u00e0o l\u1edbp 1 <\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">\u00a0B\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n con c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u1eafm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 to\u00e1n h\u1ecdc, v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c con s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ebfm<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">\u00a0B\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n con nhanh ch\u00f3ng n\u1eafm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1eb7t ch\u1eef<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">\u00a0B\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n con t\u1ef1 t\u1ea1o cho m\u00ecnh nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"_2Dia_chi_gia_su_hanh_trang_vao_lop_1_uy_tin_cho_be\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><strong>\u00a0<span style=\"color: #ed1c24;\">2.\u0110\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 gia s\u01b0 h\u00e0nh trang v\u00e0o l\u1edbp 1 uy t\u00edn cho b\u00e9<\/span><\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">\u0110\u1ed9i ng\u0169 <strong>gia s\u01b0 l\u1edbp l\u00e1<\/strong> c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-818\" src=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/gia-su\u031b-ha\u0300-no\u0323\u0302i.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"820\" height=\"312\" srcset=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/gia-su\u031b-ha\u0300-no\u0323\u0302i.png 820w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/gia-su\u031b-ha\u0300-no\u0323\u0302i-300x114.png 300w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/gia-su\u031b-ha\u0300-no\u0323\u0302i-768x292.png 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">&#8211; C\u00f3 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean l\u1edbp 1: d\u1ea1y, d\u1ed7, h\u1ecdc, ch\u01a1i<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">&#8211; R\u00e8n cho b\u00e9 th\u00f3i quen: V\u00e0o n\u1ebfp h\u1ecdc, ng\u1ed3i h\u1ecdc \u0111\u00fang, c\u00e1ch c\u1ea7m b\u00fat \u0111\u00fang.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">&#8211; Gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean luy\u1ec7n vi\u1ebft ch\u1eef \u0111\u1eb9p, \u0111\u1ecdc \u0111\u00fang, vi\u1ebft chu\u1ea9n, gh\u00e9p v\u1ea7n v\u00e0 l\u00e0m to\u00e1n nhanh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">&#8211; D\u1ea1y ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p t\u01b0 duy logic, nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft h\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc, c\u00e1ch ph\u00e2n lo\u1ea1i, nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 v\u1eadt s\u1ef1 vi\u1ec7c.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"3Bang_gia_gia_su\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #ed1c24; font-size: 100%;\"><strong>3.B\u1ea3ng gi\u00e1 gia s\u01b0<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">\n<table id=\"tablepress-27\" class=\"tablepress tablepress-id-27 tbody-has-connected-cells\">\n<tbody class=\"row-striping row-hover\">\n<tr class=\"row-1\">\n\t<td rowspan=\"2\" class=\"column-1\">L\u1edaP H\u1eccC<\/td><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"column-2\">SINH VI\u00caN<\/td><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"column-4\">GI\u00c1O VI\u00caN<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr class=\"row-2\">\n\t<td class=\"column-2\">1 h\u1ecdc sinh<\/td><td class=\"column-3\">2 h\u1ecdc sinh<\/td><td class=\"column-4\">1 h\u1ecdc sinh<\/td><td class=\"column-5\">2 h\u1ecdc sinh<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr class=\"row-3\">\n\t<td class=\"column-1\">Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb v\u00e0o l\u1edbp 1<\/td><td class=\"column-2\">120.000 \u2013 140.000<\/td><td class=\"column-3\">150.000<\/td><td class=\"column-4\">250.000<\/td><td class=\"column-5\">300.000 \u2013 350.000<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<!-- #tablepress-27 from cache --><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 Tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u1ea3ng gi\u00e1 mang t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t tham kh\u1ea3o. H\u1ecdc ph\u00ed gia s\u01b0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u00f9y theo y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a gia \u0111\u00ecnh. M\u1ecdi th\u1eafc m\u1eafc xin li\u00ean h\u1ec7 <span style=\"\">096.31.38.511<\/span> ho\u1eb7c <span style=\"\">0862.856.500<\/span>\u00a0\u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n chi ti\u1ebft h\u01a1n<\/span><\/p>\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><em><strong>****************************<\/strong><\/em><\/span><\/div>\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><em><strong>=&gt;&gt;&gt; Xem th\u00eam: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/hoc-phi-bang-gia-gia-su-tai-nha-hn-mon-toan-anh-van-hoa-ly\/\">b\u1ea3ng gi\u00e1 gia s\u01b0<\/a><\/span> \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i nh\u1ea5t, m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean b\u1ecf l\u1ee1<\/strong><\/em><\/span><\/div>\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><em><strong>=&gt;&gt;&gt; <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/bang-gia-500-gia-su-mon-toan-gioi-tu-lop-1-12-o-ha-noi\/\">Gia s\u01b0 To\u00e1n gi\u1ecfi<\/a><\/span> cam k\u1ebft con ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 sau 10 bu\u1ed5i, r\u00e8n luy\u1ec7n ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p &amp; t\u01b0 duy cho con t\u1ef1 h\u1ecdc.<\/strong><\/em><\/span><\/div>\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><em><strong>****************************<\/strong><\/em><\/span><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"4Bi_kip_tim_gia_su_cho_be_chuan_bi_vao_lop_1\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #ed1c24; font-size: 100%;\"><strong>4.B\u00ed k\u00edp t\u00ecm gia s\u01b0 cho b\u00e9 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb v\u00e0o l\u1edbp 1<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">4.1. Ti\u00eau ch\u00ed c\u1ee7a <strong>gia s\u01b0 l\u1edbp l\u00e1<\/strong> ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><em>L\u00e0 gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean ti\u1ec3u h\u1ecdc t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u00a0c\u1ea5p 1<\/em><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><em>L\u00e0 sinh vi\u00ean khoa SP ti\u1ec3u h\u1ecdc \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecdc qua c\u00e1c l\u1edbp r\u00e8n ch\u1eef , c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0111i d\u1ea1y<\/em><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><em>Ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn, t\u1eadn t\u00e2m v\u00e0 y\u00eau tr\u1ebb .\u200b<\/em><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1387\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1387\" style=\"width: 1280px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1387\" src=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/kinh-nghiem-lua-chon-gia-su-phu-hop-cho-con-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" srcset=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/kinh-nghiem-lua-chon-gia-su-phu-hop-cho-con-2.png 1280w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/kinh-nghiem-lua-chon-gia-su-phu-hop-cho-con-2-300x169.png 300w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/kinh-nghiem-lua-chon-gia-su-phu-hop-cho-con-2-768x432.png 768w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/kinh-nghiem-lua-chon-gia-su-phu-hop-cho-con-2-1024x576.png 1024w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1387\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Kinh nghi\u1ec7m l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn gia s\u01b0 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho con h\u1ecdc t\u1ed1t<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">4.2. \u0110\u1ed9i ng\u0169 <strong>gia s\u01b0 l\u1edbp l\u00e1<\/strong> c\u1ee7a trung t\u00e2m <strong>gia s\u01b0 B\u00ecnh Minh<\/strong>:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">\u00a0L\u00e0 gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean khoa Gi\u00e1o D\u1ee5c Ti\u1ec3u H\u1ecdc tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110HSP, gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng ti\u1ec3u h\u1ecdc.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">Gia s\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p khoa Gi\u00e1o D\u1ee5c Ti\u1ec3u H\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110HSP H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\"><strong>Gia s\u01b0 l\u1edbp l\u00e1<\/strong> c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3 n\u0103m kinh nghi\u1ec7m trong gia s\u01b0 cho c\u00e1c b\u00e9 m\u1eabu gi\u00e1o<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">\u00a0Gia s\u01b0 c\u00f3 t\u00ednh ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn t\u1ed1t<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">\u00a0Gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean y\u00eau ngh\u1ec1, m\u1ebfn tr\u1ebb, nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh trong c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">\u00a0Gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m s\u01b0 ph\u1ea1m ti\u1ec3u h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 c\u00f3 ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"5Quyen_loi_khi_den_voi_trung_tam\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #ed1c24; font-size: 100%;\"><strong>5.Quy\u1ec1n l\u1ee3i khi \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi trung t\u00e2m<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\">&#8211; \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecdc th\u1eed 2 bu\u1ed5i <strong>gia s\u01b0 l\u1edbp l\u00e1<\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">&#8211; T\u01b0 v\u1ea5n, gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u <strong>gia s\u01b0 d\u1ea1y k\u00e8m chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb v\u00e0o l\u1edbp 1<\/strong> ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p theo y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a gia \u0111\u00ecnh<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">&#8211; Gia \u0111\u00ecnh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed5i gia s\u01b0 n\u1ebfu c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p d\u1ea1y c\u1ee7a gia s\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">&#8211; Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i cam k\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng thu b\u1ea5t k\u00ec kho\u1ea3n ph\u00ed n\u00e0o khi t\u00ecm gia s\u01b0 cho b\u00e9<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">&#8211; \u0110\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh c\u00f9ng b\u00e9 m\u1ecdi l\u00fac m\u1ecdi n\u01a1i, l\u1eafng nghe chia s\u1ebb cu\u1ea3 ph\u1ee5 huynh b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 l\u00fac n\u00e0o v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p th\u1eafc m\u1eafc cho gia \u0111\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 gia s\u01b0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">********************************<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><em><strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\">=&gt;&gt;&gt; Xem th\u00eam:<\/span> <span style=\"color: #3366ff;\"><a style=\"color: #3366ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/top-3000-gia-su-tieng-anh-tai-nha-tang-hieu-qua-gap-5-lan\/\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">Gia s\u01b0 Ti\u1ebfng Anh<\/span><\/a><\/span> <span style=\"color: #000000;\">&#8211; Gia s\u01b0 chuy\u00ean Anh, Ph\u00e1t \u00c2m chu\u1ea9n cho con n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc ngay t\u1eeb ban \u0111\u1ea7u.<\/span><\/strong><\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>&gt;&gt;&gt; Xem ngay:\u00a0TOP 300+<\/strong>\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/bang-gia-gia-su-luyen-chu-dep-tai-nha-tien-bo-chi-sau-1-thang\/\">gia s\u01b0 luy\u1ec7n ch\u1eef \u0111\u1eb9p t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0<\/a><\/span>,\u00a0<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>ch\u1eef \u0111\u1eb9p ch\u1ec9 sau 1 kho\u00e1 h\u1ecdc.<\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">********************************<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #ed1c24; font-size: 100%;\"><strong>TRUNG T\u00c2M\u00a0GIA S\u01af\u00a0B\u00ccNH MINH<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<ul class=\"ul1\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<li class=\"li2\">\n<p class=\"footer-text\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\"><strong>C\u01a1 s\u1edf 1: N03, S\u1ed1 38-40 Tr\u1ea7n Qu\u00fd Ki\u00ean, C\u1ea7u Gi\u1ea5y, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"li2\">\n<p class=\"footer-text\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\"><strong>C\u01a1 s\u1edf 2: 583 Nguy\u1ec5n Tr\u00e3i, Thanh Xu\u00e2n, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"li2\">\n<p class=\"footer-text\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\"><strong>C\u01a1 s\u1edf 3: 479 L\u0129nh Nam, Ho\u00e0ng Mai, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p class=\"p2\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\"><b>==&gt; Hotline (24\/7): 096.31.38.511 \u2013 0862.856.500<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>GIA S\u01af B\u00ccNH MINH THU\u1ed8C HTCON VI\u1ec6T NAM GIA S\u01af L\u1edaP L\u00c1, CHU\u1ea8N B\u1eca V\u00c0O L\u1edaP 1 &#8211; GIA S\u01af S\u01af PH\u1ea0M T\u1ea0I H\u00c0 N\u1ed8I D\u1ea0Y TH\u1eec 02 BU\u1ed4I \u0110\u1ea6U [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":3336,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[463],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-3193","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-hanh-trang-lop-1-mb"],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v25.8 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>[H\u1ecdc ph\u00ed \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i] Gia s\u01b0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb v\u00e0o l\u1edbp 1 \u2013 Cho con n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc!<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Gia s\u01b0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb v\u00e0o l\u1edbp 1 v\u1edbi h\u1ecdc ph\u00ed si\u00eau \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i. Gia s\u01b0 s\u01b0 ph\